CustomField.description: Stores the Id of Business Hours to use. It is only applicable when Working Hours field has "Business Hours" selected as its value. When applied, the selected business hours are used for this user's working hours calculations elsewhere in Q-assign.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Select the Id of Business Hours to use. It is only applicable when Working Hours field has "Business Hours" selected as its value. When applied, the selected business hours are used for this user's working hours calculations elsewhere in Q-assign.
CustomField.label: Business Hours (No Longer Used)
